Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要过来 不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:11.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退后 我叫你们退后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把枪放下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西不是你能拿的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫你不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:20.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:36.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子弹是拿出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.43,0:02:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过拯救他已经没有生命危险
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是能不能够醒过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经完全是属于植物人状况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本连自己走动都不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)}第三夜 逃走的男子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.29,0:04:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是漂亮的夕阳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.28,0:04:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用亲眼看到那最后真正的太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:42.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:45.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远的黒暗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.83,0:04:50.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤 让我赐给你永远
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:59.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.65,0:05:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么好害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这冰冷的黑暗中你的出现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤 你只要跟着我走就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生 紫藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那个时候没遇见那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会在冰冷黑暗的夜晚中徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这些血腥的战斗就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.40,0:05:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤 这不是你所期望的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远的光和永远的黑暗共同存在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理保
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很无趣吧 和我约会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.38,0:06:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生一直都是很严肃的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 理保 因为在想些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是紫藤先生从刚才就很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:38.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很便宜 才三千 三千
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:44.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:49.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服输了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被别人笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 因为是紫藤先生送的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.21,0:07:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次换我送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.69,0:07:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要什么东西 不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.61,0:07:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.89,0:07:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我想送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生你的生日是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开 不准动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 在街上拿这么危险的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.68,0:07:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是你干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃 大家快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜灵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.78,0:08:29.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.32,0:08:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄金的黎明快要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的时代将要来临
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:46.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要仔细去看 紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.91,0:08:47.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能 刚才是界…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在地下街追夜灵的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是新宿的警察
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们的死亡报告已经出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察局认为有危险 正在寻找夜灵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有光的地方就有黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:35.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身处于光那里的人就假装不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为什么现在出现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道他一直在黒暗中观察我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.66,0:09:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 到底是发生什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:56.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:10:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你出去后的紫藤就一直那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们发生什么事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是因为我的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.73,0:10:08.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.78,0:10:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事情也没有 昨天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个色色女人头里到底在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 谁是色色女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就讲有什么没发生过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私家侦探的紫藤先生在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:39.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:42.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日子也已经选好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他却突然失踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 请你去找别家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:51.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这里也有些事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道很勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.69,0:10:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我已经没有别的地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:59.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说紫藤先生一定会有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生 这个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.76,0:11:17.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚见过面 最近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的名字叫泷隆一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,职业是警察
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上个月因为调查事件时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被手枪击中后突然失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后又突然出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内部的出丑 难怪警察会如此拼命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一点都没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你们 在警察抓到他之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请保护隆一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.25,0:11:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果还没有完全被夜灵控制住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.11,0:11:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就还有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:58.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真好心 有没有感觉热心过头
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许对美女没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.96,0:12:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果对女人太好 小心会遭天遣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生这样讲 我也不敢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底隐藏些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会被你知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不是夜灵的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以有必要去证明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个危险的约会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隆一真的会在这种地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:51.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照我的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.48,0:12:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他应该就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:56.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里比在地面上安全
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.99,0:13:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是他逃脱的附近地点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且现在没有被使用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个藏身的好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有阳光冰冷的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:17.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有阴湿陪伴着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真像是个鬼屋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个约会最佳地点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.89,0:14:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:09.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥生 在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 隆一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.58,0:14:22.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:25.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惠小姐 他已经不是隆一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.67,0:14:28.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 他…隆一他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你拉出来　
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.10,0:14:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.35,0:14:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到黑暗里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤 危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.96,0:15:03.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你别做蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隆一 站起来 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 镇定一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.49,0:15:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是我家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是辛苦 要把你带到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是太好了 你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 你想吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有要帮你买换洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隆一 振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口会裂开的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:37.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隆一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.25,0:16:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了 没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以拜托你别再离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再离开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄金的黎明开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.26,0:17:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个病人完全变成植物人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.63,0:17:31.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通根本不可能自己走动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.42,0:17:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能够讲详细一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,患者头部受到枪伤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:41.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好没有伤害到脑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是还是没有意识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.84,0:17:47.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真的死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:50.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然身体还在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是灵魂已经远离肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:57.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以夜灵就进入那个肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:00.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷在捜査中失踪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是警察捏造的 根本就是骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他当成样品秘密的收起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送到NOS的事件都是些大事件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界 他到底在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.65,0:18:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是松永
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！找到泷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:52.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.18,0:19:06.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点 泷的意识应该没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:08.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女人会有危险
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.89,0:19:09.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见 紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.12,0:19:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.93,0:19:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泷 投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.69,0:19:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底犯了什么错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是射击组 瞄准准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:04.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隆一什么事情都没有做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:05.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.38,0:20:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准许射击 只瞄准男的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:09.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:12.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:16.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要来妨碍我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.03,0:20:19.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隆一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隆一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.24,0:20:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤 我希望你不要管这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底隐藏些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么现在要回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候你就会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄金的黎明就要来临
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:20:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄金的黎明？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:03.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有那个义务要去看着它
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.58,0:21:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:14.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤在变成吸血鬼之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说 人类以前的事情记不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.94,0:21:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的父母的脸 出生地点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连自己真正的名字也不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丧失记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.85,0:21:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他认为我是成为吸血鬼最佳的人选
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 他是唯一知道我过去的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直都很想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:52.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 我讲错话了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.87,0:21:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问他生日是什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:22:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些事他都没有跟我讲过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.02,0:22:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你讲也没有用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.62,0:22:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.86,0:22:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许他想没事的和理保交往
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.91,0:22:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.22,0:22:24.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.00,0:22:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 我不能放着夜灵不管
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.06,0:22:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心 我一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.01,0:22:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.89,0:22:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.14,0:23:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不逃吗 泷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.02,0:23:28.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为夜灵 要离开那肉体对你来讲很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.35,0:23:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.05,0:24:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不变回夜灵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.73,0:24:10.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.33,0:24:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙根本不想变回夜灵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.89,0:24:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成为人类的样子死去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.30,0:24:41.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快一点 天就要亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.65,0:24:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄金的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.82,0:24:47.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.75,0:26:29.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我也能变成大人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.24,0:26:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种夜晚也许就不会那么寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.68,0:26:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Night Walker 第四夜
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.20,0:26:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄金的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.85,0:26:41.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不想要…什么永远
